Implemented H07 fixes and wrote the required report to `.review-slices/H07.fix.md`.

Applied six narrow fixes across `packages/common`, `packages/consensus`, `packages/effect`, and `packages/errors`. Deferred the chain preset/Mainnet-Prague issue as too risky for an automatic patch because it needs explicit per-chain EthereumJS config and hardfork policy.

Per constraints, I did not run tests, builds, package managers, or git commands.
